列表到底末尾位置时触发。
事件名称：onReachEnd
事件参数：{}
事件返回值：None
列表元素发生移动时触发。
事件名称：onItemMove
事件参数：{'from': {"type":"number","required":true,"description":"移动前索引值。","default":null}, 'to': {"type":"number","required":true,"description":"移动后索引值。","default":null}}
事件返回值：None
绑定该事件的列表元素可作为拖拽释放目标，当在列表元素内停止拖拽时触发。
事件名称：onItemDrop
事件参数：{'event': {"type":"ItemDragInfo","required":true,"description":"拖拽点的信息。","default":null}, 'itemIndex': {"type":"number","required":true,"description":"拖拽起始位置。","default":null}, 'insertIndex': {"type":"number","required":true,"description":"拖拽插入位置。","default":null}, 'isSuccess': {"type":"boolean","required":true,"description":"是否成功释放","default":null}}
事件返回值：None
当List组件在编辑模式时，点击ListItem右边出现的删除按钮时触发。从API version9开始废弃不再使用，无替代接口。
事件名称：onItemDelete
事件参数：{'index': {"type":"number","required":true,"description":"被删除的列表项的索引值。","default":null}}
事件返回值：None
设置List组件的布局列数或行数。gutter为列间距，当列数大于1时生效。
属性名称：lanes
属性参数：{'value': {"type":["number",{"minLength":"number","maxLength":"number"}],"required":true,"description":"List组件的布局列数或行数。","default":null}, 'gutter': {"type":"Dimension","required":false,"description":"列间距。","default":null}}

